  <div id="main">

    <article class="left-side">
      <%= image_tag "trailer.jpg" %>
      <section>
        <h1>Opening May 2nd, 2015</h1>
        <p>How about a refreshing shaved ice?  Find us in the
          parking lot of
          <a href="http://kamasfoodtown.com", target="_blank">Kamas Foodtown</a>
          in the heart of beautiful Kamas, Utah.
        </p>
        <div class="inner-section">
          <p>Mon-Fri:&nbsp; 2pm - 7pm<br/>
          Sat:&nbsp; 11am - 7pm</p>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-section">
          <p>146 W. 200 S.<br/>
            Kamas, UT  84036<br/>
            <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?ll=40.640565,-111.283697&z=12&t=m&hl=en-US&gl=US&mapclient=embed&q=146%20W%20200%20S%20Kamas%2C%20UT%2084036", target="_blank">view on google maps</a>
          </p>
      </section>
    </article>

    <article class="right-side">
      <%= image_tag "avalanche.jpg" %>
      <section>
        <h1>The Avalanche</h1>
        <p>You're looking at the Peach Cobbler
          Avalanche... vanilla ice cream, Georgia Peach shaved ice, smothered in
          heavy cream. Two words:
          <em>brain freeze</em>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>

    <article class="left-side">
      <%= image_tag "snow_artists.jpg" %>
      <section>
        <h1>Snow Artists</h1>
        <p>You may see an empty foam cup and a block of ice.  We see a sweet
          frozen masterpiece waiting to happen.  We love working at Kamas Snow!
          It's the coolest summer job in town.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>

    <article class="right-side last-article">
      <%= image_tag "kamas_royalty_2014.jpg" %>
      <section>
        <h1>Your Royal Highness...</h1>
        <p> The Kamas Fiesta Days royalty cooled off with shaved ice. Thanks for
          stopping by... Aly, Hailey, and Brianna.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>

